<!Practical:-Design a web page using java script to demonstrate,Alert Box,Confirm Box and 
Prompt Box>
<html>
<body>
<p>Click the button to display a confirm box.</p>
<button onclick="myFunction()">Try it</button>
<p id="demo"></p>
<script>
function myFunction() {
 var x;
 if (confirm("Press a button!") == true) {
 x = "You pressed OK!";
 } else {
 x = "You pressed Cancel!";
 }
 document.getElementById("demo").innerHTML = x;
}
</script>
</body>
</html>
